## Who is a project manager?
**A Project manager** is a starting position in an IT company, where you need to be able to listen to the team, communicate with the customer, get out of conflict situations, control the quality and implementation of the project on time and within budget.## Project manager responsibilities:
* project management as a whole;
* drawing up a work plan (design and task assigned for the team);
* team organization to work on the project;
* interview new team members, determine priorities for their successful implementation;
* create a working atmosphere in the team;
* interaction with the team and the customer;
* troubleshooting in order to complete a project on time and meet client-driven requirements.
If you don't have experience in the IT field, but you interact with people well, know how to distribute tasks in a team, and know English at a good level, we are ready to consider your candidacy. Just record a [video interview](/videointerview) and send it to us.

We consider candidates even without work experience, so do not miss your chance to start working in the IT field.

## What does a copywriter need to do?
* Write texts on a wide variety of topics, mainly in English.
* Be competent in conveying information in simple terms.
* Generate ideas.
* Just be in a good mood.
## We guarantee:
* Work from home. Work in comfortable conditions;
* An opportunity to try yourself in the new field and improve already existing skills;
* Career growth from copywriter to marketer;
* Interesting and creative tasks;
* The ability to work with foreign customers;
* Decent salary and understanding leaders.
We also offer the possibility of further training in **marketing specialties** such as **SEO**, **SMM**, and **Content Manager**. Alternatively, you can try yourself to be a **Proofreader**, **Rewriter**, **SEO-copywriter**, and **Content Manager**.
We expect your English to be above an intermediate level; you to be diligent, attentive, and ready to learn. We also expect responsibility, punctuality, creativity, and result-orientation from you.
## Copywriter Vacancy
If you think you are a suitable candidate for this job, then send us your contacts and CV as soon as possible.

## You are an ideal candidate for an accountant position if you:
* Advanced in PCs, Google Sheets, and Excel.
* Have teamwork skills.
* Your English is at B1 level and above.
## Responsibilities of an accountant include:
* payroll accounting on a monthly basis;
* accounting of customer payments;
* correspondence with customers regarding payments and profits for employees;
* sending contracts and other forms to new employees for filling;
* accounting of the company’s current expenses;
* accounting of days off and vacations of employees;
* tracking and accounting payments of our debtors;
* solving other current problems and issues.
It will be an advantage if you have experience of working with contracts and accounting source documents or have had economic education. But if not, don’t worry – we’re ready to teach you.
Record a[video interview](/videointerview) in English and we will contact you as soon as possible.

## Chat Operator Job Description
The Chat Operator is an online website consultant (an online website operator) who answers all questions from visitors and buyers in real-time. A specialist is to answer customer requests, tell customers about the website, and show where everything is located, just like any consultant in a real store.
## Main tasks of the Chat Operator
The main task of an online operatoris to answer calls or messages from a client immediately. Also, you will need to correspond with the client base, take customer queries and resolve issues on the basis of customer service standards, and provide fast, high-quality, and accurate information to customers.
## Chat Operator Requirements
* Аt least Intermediate level of English;
* Desire to work, study and develop;
* Fast typing;
* Sociability;
* To be a confident PC user.
Send us your contact details if you think you are suitable for this job.
## Ready to join?
To become part of our team, you need to record a short [video interview](/videointerview) in English and send it to us. After reviewing your resume, we will contact you for further collaboration.

Lead generation is about finding potential customers. We work in the field of B2B (business to business), and our goal is to cooperate with other companies.

The lead generation manager searches for the target audience and keeps business correspondence. It’s a completely remote job in our company.
## What is the essence of the work?
Through the rapid development of the Internet and the active usage of social networks, it has become possible to directly contact the employer and make him a business offer!
Working in various social networks and with the help of our team, the lead generator collects a database of contacts and companies, potentially or already ready for cooperation.
You will work with social networks and collect a database that contains contacts of companies and employees. You will also need to use Google Search and work with Excel spreadsheets.
We will teach you how to search effectively and help you make the right offer!
## Requirements for a lead generator are:
* Be an advanced PC user;
* Be a confident Microsoft Office user;
* Skills in searching for the necessary information;
* B1+ English level;
* Communication skills;
* Punctuality.
## We offer:
* Training and assistance at all stages of work;
* Ability to work on foreign projects;
* Career growth;
* Day shifts from 9:00 to 18:00 or evening shifts from 15:00 to 24:00;
* Timely payment + bonuses and profits.
Record [a video interview](/videointerview) and tell us about your skills and knowledge. 
Apply for the job

Fill out the application form

## Who is a Blogger?
A person who keeps his or her personal diary or journal is considered to be a blogger. But if his\her content is unique and has not been shown anywhere, blogging is a very popular job nowadays, and many people would like to try their hand in this field. We provide the opportunity and instructions.
We are pleased to announce that we have vacancies in addition to the blogger position. This is how we think of our future employees: as someone who wants to learn new things and improve their skills at work.
A blog can have a wide variety of forms: text, photos, videos, or all rolled into one. Content work is the most important thing for a blogger. The content of the blog is the key priority for bloggers. It is necessary that everything looks presentable and attracts attention.
We will teach you how to make your blog “live” and make a profit.
Our company is always aware of the current state of affairs. We have a job for bloggers! Contact us today. We are waiting for your CV!## We will help you to master the profession of a blogger
We will teach you how to **make your blog “live**” and **make a profit**.
Our company is always aware of the current state of affairs. We have a **job for bloggers**! Contact us today. We are waiting for your CV!
## Blogger vacancy required skills:
* eloquence;
* creativity;
* the ability to express your thoughts clearly and accessible;
* content planning.
## Remote job of blogger
We are loyal to all applicants and provide support when you are in the blogging position at the very beginning. The ideal candidate for us is a deeply motivated person ready to acquire new and valuable professional skills.## An online blogger should:
* Be aware of the most discussed topics in social networks;
* Adapt to “your” subscriber;
* Be able to interest and retain the target audience;
* Be creative;
* Have good communication skills.
